      <title>英国右翼改革党提出改革英国央行量化宽松计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/uk-s-right-wing-reform-party-floats-overhaul-of-boe-s-qe-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国叛乱右翼政党改革英国希望改革英格兰银行的印钞计划，以节省数十亿英镑用于履行宣言承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/uk-s-right-wing-reform-party-floats-overhaul-of-boe-s-qe-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 19:18:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙在欧盟投票失败后呼吁举行法国立法选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/macron-calls-french-legislative-elections-after-eu-vote-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲议会投票中，极右翼政党击败了法国和德国的主流政党，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙宣布提前举行立法选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/macron-calls-french-legislative-elections-after-eu-vote-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 19:08:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多将于本周就有争议的税收改革进行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/trudeau-to-call-vote-on-contentious-tax-change-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府将于本周就提高资本利得税纳入税率的计划进行投票，此举将为政府带来数十亿美元的额外收入，并引起了商界的愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/trudeau-to-call-vote-on-contentious-tax-change-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 18:50:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙和肖尔茨在欧盟选举中败给极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/macron-s-group-thrashed-by-far-right-le-pen-s-party-in-eu-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙和德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨在周日的欧洲议会选举中遭遇惨败，极右翼政党取得的进展可能会导致欧盟在移民问题上采取更强硬的立场，并扰乱保护气候的雄心勃勃的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/macron-s-group-thrashed-by-far-right-le-pen-s-party-in-eu-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 18:05:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甘茨因总理未能满足要求而辞去以色列政府职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/israel-s-gantz-quits-war-cabinet-after-ultimatum-to-netanyahu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本尼·甘茨在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击之后加入以色列执政联盟，组建紧急战时政府。他表示，由于总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡未能满足他的要求，他的政党将退出政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/israel-s-gantz-quits-war-cabinet-after-ultimatum-to-netanyahu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:54:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>出口民调显示保加利亚前总理鲍里索夫赢得临时投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/bulgarian-ex-premier-borissov-wins-snap-vote-exit-poll-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚实力强大的前总理博伊科·鲍里索夫有望赢得该国三年多来的第六次选举，但未能获得结束政治僵局所需的多数票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/bulgarian-ex-premier-borissov-wins-snap-vote-exit-poll-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨领导的德国社会民主党在欧盟投票中遭遇创纪录的惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/scholz-s-party-suffers-historic-rout-in-german-eu-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党在周日的欧洲议会选举中遭遇史上最差成绩，落后于极右翼的德国选择党，位居第三。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/scholz-s-party-suffers-historic-rout-in-german-eu-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 16:04:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰重建最高官员错失关键职位 德国论坛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/ukraine-war-top-reconstruction-official-to-miss-key-german-forum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于内部政治争吵，乌克兰负责重建的最高官员将缺席今年的捐助方展示会议，这可能会给人留下这样一种印象：重建并不是基辅的首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/ukraine-war-top-reconstruction-official-to-miss-key-german-forum</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 16:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列人在救援中得到喘息，但战争的挑战依然存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/israel-hamas-war-gaza-hostage-rescue-celebrated-even-as-challenges-endure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他们在街上跳舞，在海滩上欢呼，电视主播在镜头前泪流满面。周六，四名人质从加沙中部获救，以色列举行了罕见而热烈的庆祝活动，为本雅明·内塔尼亚胡政府和陷入困境的军队注入了新的活力。这场艰苦的战争已经持续了八个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/israel-hamas-war-gaza-hostage-rescue-celebrated-even-as-challenges-endure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 11:05:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士支持发展绿色能源，拒绝医疗保险上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/swiss-voters-back-more-green-energy-reject-health-insurance-cap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士选民支持政府推动国内可再生能源发展的计划，这一决定将使在阿尔卑斯山建设太阳能和风能发电厂变得更加容易，并确保继续提供补贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/swiss-voters-back-more-green-energy-reject-health-insurance-cap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 10:11:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
